.TH PRODBOX_aws 1
.SH NAME
prodbox-aws \- AWS IAM and quota management
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B prodbox aws
.SH DESCRIPTION
Operational AWS administration commands.
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
\fBpolicy\fR
Render IAM policy JSON
.TP
\fBsetup\fR
Create or refresh operational IAM user
.TP
\fBteardown\fR
Delete operational IAM user
.TP
\fBcheck-quotas\fR
Inspect supported AWS quotas
.TP
\fBrequest-quotas\fR
Request supported AWS quotas
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
\fBprodbox aws policy\fR
Inspect the IAM policy without mutating AWS.
